  .title Archives

  %p Archives provides access to descriptions and finding aids for more than 5,500 archival collections in six Columbia repositories.

  %p Archival collections include personal papers, institutional records, corporate archives, architectural drawings, printed ephemera, realia, and many other types of content.

  %p This source searches:
  %ul
    %li finding aids
    %li collection descriptions
    %li available digital content, such as online exhibits and images



